snippet.title: Diana and Roma make their own Valentine's card
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma enlist the help of their friends from around the world to create the ultimate Valentine.
Parents, find out more about Love, Diana dolls, playsets, roleplay @ Target below!

Love, Diana Plush Doll: http://bit.ly/35EzGUY​
Love, Diana at Target: http://bit.ly/3aSRTzA

With Valentine's Day quickly approaching, it's more important than ever to share the love! And there is no better way to share the love than to make your very own Valentine's card.
Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx​
